              <p>A Holiday at home for older people, 30th, 31st Aug, 1st Sept, 10.30am-3.30pm, £6 a day, including lunch. Booking Forms are now available from All Saints Parish Office in Onslow Gardens. If you or anyone you know would like to come along and join in the fun, food and fellowship, please fill in a form and return it with payment to the Parish Office, All Saints Church, Onslow Gardens CR2 9AB. For more information please telephone 020 8657 0665.</p>
